Author: Dan from Minter
Title: ⚡️ Instant & Absolute Liquidity: BIP Early Access Campaign Announcement ⚡️
Body: Dear Bitcointalk community members,  The Minter team is pleased to announce that you can now apply for taking part in the early access campaign designed to distribute BIP—our blockchain network’s native digital coin. For that, you will first need to pass the KYC/AML check (it’s super fast and processed through Telegram Passport). Please note that residents of the U.S. and China are not eligible for participation.  For more detail about our early access campaign, visit this page: https://minter.network/ps  Now, what is Minter? Below are just a few competitive advantages Minter has over other projects:     For more information about Minter, read the white paper: https://about.minter.network/Minter_White_Paper.pdf?v02  You can also visit the official website: https://www.minter.network or Telegram channel: https://t.me/MinterTeam  Should you have any questions, you are more than welcome to ask them either here or via Telegram bot: https://t.me/minterhelpbot
